<h2 class="bold font-l">Cinderella's Dress (1950)</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The classic version, the Fairy Godmother gifts the Princess to be a magical dress for the ball. Bibbidi-bobbidi-boo! </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GorgeousGarmentGeneration" class='trope-example-link'>Gorgeous Garment Generation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Walt Disney Animation Studios</span>, <span>Walt Disney Feature Animation</span> </h3>
